"""
SNN Ensemble Emergence Experiment
=================================
Tests whether intrinsic diversity in spiking neural networks produces
emergent collective capabilities that no individual network possesses.

Designed for Google Colab (GPU runtime).
Based on Sergiy's SNN-ANN hybrid triage research.

Key questions:
1. At what N do emergent outputs appear (ensemble right, all individuals wrong)?
2. How does error decorrelation scale with N?
3. Can disagreement patterns detect out-of-distribution inputs?
4. At what N does cost exceed single ANN?

Run: Open in Colab, set runtime to GPU, run all cells.
"""

